title: Gitte Krogh
text:
Gitte Krogh (born 13 May 1977) is a former Danish female <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a>. She was part of the <a href="Denmark%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Denmark women's national football team</a>.
She competed at the <a href="Football%20at%20the%201996%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Women%27s%20tournament">1996 Summer Olympics</a>, playing 3 matches.
